The earth is in danger.
Global warming or collision with a killer asteroid.
Caravans of spaceships with Earthlings on board go in search of a spare planet.
In order to preserve humanity, the main question arises, how to continue its kind in the conditions of weightlessness or on the same reserve planet?
I think the choice is small.
